Beſides, the Ships could not furniſh the Army with more Men or Victuals:
wherefore I underſtand not in what Reſpect his going up was neceſſary;
and yet the Fleet muſt have endured many Hazards to this little purpoſe.

The Purſer of her was taken, and by Threats compell'd to tell of another
of their Company behind, that had Order to fall with that Iſland;
and gave us ſuch particular Advertiſement, that indeed ſhe fell to be ours.
